data.description:
Introducing to you this beautiful 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home located in a quiet cul-de-sac neighborhood.
 Easy access to freeway and schools. 
 Seller owned solar!! Vaulted ceilings, tile flooring throughout the entire home.
 Lovely Master bedroom with double sided fireplace, separate seating area, his/hers closets. Sprinkler system in front and back yard and much more. 
 Schedule your appointment today, come on by take a look and fall in love!!
